workflow.name: Automated business KPI insights with GPT-4, MSSQL, analytics & multi-channel alerts
workflow.description:
## WORKFLOW OVERVIEW

This workflow is an AI-powered business intelligence agent designed for founders and business owners.
It automatically collects key business metrics, calculates performance KPIs, applies decision logic, uses AI reasoning, and sends clear, actionable notifications ‚Äî without dashboards or manual reports.

## Key Features:

‚úÖ Aggregates multiple data sources (MSSQL, Google Analytics, Google Sheets)
‚úÖ Calculates critical KPIs: ROAS, CAC, Revenue & User Growth
‚úÖ Applies rule-based decision logic for business risk and opportunity detection
‚úÖ AI-powered reasoning: summarizes insights and recommends actions
‚úÖ Multi-channel notifications: Email, WhatsApp, Slack, Telegram
‚úÖ Fully automated daily execution via Cron trigger
‚úÖ Enterprise-ready: error handling, structured data, KPI validation

## Setup & Requirements:


- API access to data sources (MSSQL, Google Analytics, Google Sheets)
- OpenAI or Google Gemini API for AI reasoning
- Messaging integration: Gmail, Twilio (WhatsApp), Slack, Telegram
- 
## Workflow Flow:

- Cron Trigger ‚Äì runs daily at a chosen time
- Data Collection ‚Äì revenue, users, marketing spend, website analytics
- Merge Node ‚Äì combines all data sources
- Function Node ‚Äì consolidates into a single JSON object
- KPI Calculation ‚Äì calculates ROAS, CAC, growth rates
- Business Logic Engine ‚Äì identifies risks and opportunities
- AI Reasoning Agent ‚Äì summarizes insights, suggests actions
- Notification Formatter ‚Äì builds founder-friendly message
- Notification Delivery ‚Äì sends via WhatsApp, Email, Slack, or Telegram

## Example Data Formation

These data below Getting from all different channels.

`{
  "revenue": 4290,
  "registeredUsers": 20,
  "totalUsers": 3,
  "adSpend": 800
}`

Applies rule-based logic to detect potential risks or opportunities

`{
  "ROAS": 5.36,
  "CAC": 40,
  "agentStatus": "normal",
  "agentPriority": "low",
  "insights": ["Marketing campaigns are performing very well"]
}`

## Workflow Highlights

Fully automated, runs daily without human intervention
Integrates multiple business data sources
Converts raw data into KPIs for actionable insight
Applies both rule-based logic and AI reasoning
Generates concise, human-friendly notifications
Sending notification to different channels.

Your job:

parameters.subject: Yesterday's Revenue Report

parameters.content:
## OVERVIEW


This workflow is an AI-powered business intelligence agent designed for founders and business owners.
It automatically collects key business metrics, calculates performance KPIs, applies decision logic, uses AI reasoning, and sends clear, actionable notifications ‚Äî without dashboards or manual reports.


## Architecture

Scheduler
 ‚Üí Data Collection (MSSQL, Analytics, Sheets)
 ‚Üí Merge Results
 ‚Üí Data Consolidation
 ‚Üí KPI Calculation
 ‚Üí Business Decision Logic
 ‚Üí AI Reasoning Agent
 ‚Üí Notification Formatter
 ‚Üí Smart Alerts (WhatsApp / Email / Slack)


## Setup & Requirements:

API access to data sources (MSSQL, Google Analytics, Google Sheets)
OpenAI or Google Gemini API for AI reasoning
Messaging integration: Gmail, Twilio (WhatsApp), Slack, Telegram

## Notification Formatter

Prepare a professional message with AI summary and key statistics for distributions. 

Finally, you can deliver the output with multiple communication channels:

Gmail / SMTP Node ‚Üí For Email
Twilio / WhatsApp Cloud API Node ‚Üí For WhatsApp
Slack / Telegram Node ‚Üí Optional team notifications

## DATA EXTRACTION

1. Fetches yesterday‚Äôs total revenue from the database.
2. Fetches number of newly registered users for yesterday.
3. Fetches total users for yesterday to measure traffic and engagement.
4. Fetches yesterday‚Äôs marketing expenses (manual or automated source).
5. Combines all incoming data sources into a single execution context.

## DATA CHECKER

1. After getting all data need to check if data available using IF nodes
2. If data is not available send email to dedication person for verify the data
3. Make sure you are getting all data sources from all nodes. don't allow to execute next step without getting any one fail.

## DATA NORMALIZE

1. Converts raw data into a consistent format and correct data types for calculation.
2. Ensures reliable calculation and avoids error due to inconsistent data types.
3. These node will return total amount of revenue, Total users registered, total users visited and total amount spend for marketing.

## COMBINE REPORTS
1. Merge all datasets into one unified dataset for calculation
2. Allows side-by-side comparison of today's and yesterday's metrics
3. The Data Consolidation Function Node transforms the merged multiple items into one structured JSON object.
4. Key performance indicators that provide actionable insights for founders
5. Business logic node will applies rule basic logic to detect the potential risks or opportunities for marketing.

This will show you the indications that if marketing is inefficiency and if high acquisition cost and if strong campaign performance.

## AI SUMMARY GENERATION
1. Using OpenAI to generate a human friendly summary of traffic changes and produce insights automatically without manual works.

This will generate concise business summary, identifies risks and opportunities

you can change the system prompt based on your requirements and you can change the LLM which you like.

data.details:
The IF node can be used to implement binary conditional logic in your workflow. You can set up one-to-many conditions to evaluate each item of data being inputted into the node. That data will either evaluate to TRUE or FALSE and route out of the node accordingly.

This node has multiple types of conditions: Bool, String, Number, and Date & Time.
